<!-- Accordion -->
<div id="accordion-collapse" data-accordion="collapse">
  <!-- Primera pregunta -->
  <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
    <button
      type="button"
      class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right border border-b-0 bg-white border-gray-700 text-dark rounded-t-lg hover:bg-zinc-100 gap-3 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
      data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-1"
      aria-expanded="false"
      aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-1"
    >
      <span class="text-dark">¿Cuántas especialidades tienen?</span>
      <svg
        data-accordion-icon
        class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300"
        aria-hidden="true"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 10 6"
      >
        <path
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"
        ></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </h2>
  <div
    id="accordion-collapse-body-1"
    class="hidden"
    aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-1"
  >
    <div class="font-semibold p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-700 bg-gray-50">
      <p class="mb-2 text-dark">
        Las especialidades que ofrecemos en la Unidad Educativa <span class="text-blue-600">Alessandro Volta</span> son:
        <ol class="list-inside list-decimal text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li>Electricidad</li>
          <li>Mecánica</li>
          <li>Automotriz</li>
          <li>Electrónica</li>
          <li>Informática</li>
          <li>Comercialización y Ventas</li>
          <li>Ciencias Generales</li>
        </ol>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Segunda pregunta -->
  <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-2">
    <button
      type="button"
      class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right border border-t-1 bg-white border-gray-700 text-dark border-inherit hover:bg-zinc-100 gap-3 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
      data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-2"
      aria-expanded="false"
      aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-2"
    >
      <span class="text-dark">¿Cómo obtengo mi matrícula automática?</span>
      <svg
        data-accordion-icon
        class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300"
        aria-hidden="true"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 10 6"
      >
        <path
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"
        ></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </h2>
  <div
    id="accordion-collapse-body-2"
    class="hidden"
    aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-2"
  >
    <div class="font-semibold p-5 border border-b-1 border-gray-700 rounded-b-lg bg-gray-50">
      <p class="text-dark">
        Para obtener la <span class="text-blue-600">matrícula automática</span>, sigue estos pasos:
        <ol class="list-inside list-decimal text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li>Revisar los requisitos</li>
          <li>Visitar la institución</li>
          <li>Completar el formulario de matrícula</li>
          <li>Confirmar la matrícula</li>
        </ol>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

